skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Cancelled
Cancelled --> Pending : approve
Cancelled : entry / log post
Pending --> Delivered : reject
Pending : entry / log post
Delivered --> Rejected : update
Rejected --> Draft : submit
Rejected : entry / log post
Draft --> Archived : submit
Archived --> [*]
@enduml